How to build tcs on Linux
-------------------------

make -f makefile.linux tcs

How to build tcs on Solaris
---------------------------

make -f makefile.solaris tcs

How to build tcs on Windows NT (MS VC++)
----------------------------------------

1. Edit makefile.nt_ms as follows:

   INTERBASE variable should point to a directory where
   InterBase kit is installed, e.g.:

   INTERBASE=d:\InterBase

2. make -f makefile.nt_ms tcs.exe

How to build tcs on SINIX-Z
---------------------------

make -f makefile.sinixz tcs
